```class Solution {
    public String licenseKeyFormatting(String s, int k) {
        s = s.replaceAll("-|\\s", "").toUpperCase();
        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
        int count = 0;
        for (int i = s.length() - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
            sb.append(s.charAt(i));
            count++;
            if (count == k) {
                sb.append("-");
                count = 0;
            }
        }
        return sb.reverse().toString();
    }
}```
